{"tid":758090,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"又鼻炎聞唔到野，可否唔食抗生素等佢自己好？","createTime":"2018-07-27T11:13:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-27T17:55:54.000Z","uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ddd2febc57a9c79300ccaa0c332e164145f75fd7","tid":758090,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T11:13:02.000Z","msg":"我剛剛傷風完，個鼻就聞唔到野（人生中第三次），<br />\n連屎味，煙味都完全聞唔到，<br />\n抆完屎張廁紙控到個鼻前面都聞唔到，<br />\n本身想去睇醫生，<br />\n但係過去兩年既經驗令我唔想去：<br />\n<br />\n2016: 第一次傷風後聞唔到野，去卓健睇耳鼻喉專科，個醫生照完內窺鏡都睇唔到野，只係比抗生素我食，咁抗生素實好啦，食三日就冇事<br />\n<br />\n2017: 第二次傷風後聞唔到野，去家庭醫生分享番上次經驗，叫佢開抗生素，食三日又冇事<br />\n<br />\n比我感覺上好似連醫生都唔會睇到d咩<br />\n只會開抗生素<br />\n各位ching，咁我仲去唔去睇好？<br />\n會唔會自己慢慢好番架？<br />\n年年咁食抗生素好危險？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：每日有鹽水噴劑洗鼻，多鼻水時有食telfast"},{"pid":"354cf01a103f649e3411c56c801ca405640729ab","tid":758090,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T13:07:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f56b061d371e17e2f25cdba6ddcccff0234cfc8","tid":758090,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T13:08:22.000Z","msg":"洗鼻會唔會好D?"},{"pid":"005d12a58a36b979d7cd749bd95bfbe19ba4703e","tid":758090,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T13:22:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>洗鼻會唔會好D?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n暫時冇咩起息，初步諗住洗多一星期先，都唔得就睇醫生食抗生素"},{"pid":"3401fc26a797b213ac745953dcc34df049b9dc14","tid":758090,"uid":173603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T13:28:07.000Z","msg":"食中藥好過"},{"pid":"b43cb2f9cff856a3e0e85c7f55df75ac724c25fc","tid":758090,"uid":27008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3401fc26a797b213ac745953dcc34df049b9dc14","tid":758090,"uid":173603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T13:28:07.000Z","msg":"食中藥好過"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T15:48:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d052b293caf8625ce7ed1fb26bbd64f787071e3a","tid":758090,"uid":27008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T15:50:42.000Z","msg":"其實一年一次唔算多<br />\n咁後生，可以靠身體打下先，暫時食住d symptoms relieve 既藥，打唔贏先好食antibiotics<br />\n所以樓主你算係正確態度"},{"pid":"c2e45fafec7e6dea6375de1295fa7032fe7f9e4a","tid":758090,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T17:55:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實一年一次唔算多<br />\n咁後生，可以靠身體打下先，暫時食住d symptoms relieve 既藥，打唔贏先好食antibiotics<br />\n所以樓主你算係正確態度</blockquote><br />\n希望打贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2743215dd1943e6a45a382a4f98ee3b68e2c8fdd","tid":758090,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T17:55:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食中藥好過</blockquote><br />\n有冇邊間推介 一直唔知點入手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}